The paper deals with logic and reasoning in games, which falls under the category of mathematical logic (cs.LO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of annotated formulas, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of proof transformations, which is a topic in machine learning and computational learning theory (cs.LG). The paper also deals with sequent calculus, which is a topic in computational complexity (cs.CC) and programming languages (cs.PL).
